               <p>ISRAEL LYONS. I live in Middlesex-street; I lodged my things in the house of Mr. Joseph. I only come to prove the property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18140914-25-person309">
                  ESTHER 
                  JOSEPH
               <interp inst="t18140914-25-person309" type="surname" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
